    "body": "This is a piece of #21088 split out for more focused review.\n\nThese are the only changes to v1's flash_attn backend to support\ncross-attention.\n\n1. Remove the block on ENCODER_DECODER attention.\n\n2. Handle the fact that `key` and `value` may be `None`. These are set\n   the first time the decoder runs, but for subsequent runs, they come\n   from KV cache only.\n\nSigned-off-by: Russell Bryant <rbryant@redhat.com>\n",
